<HL>
   International Controls
</HL>
<DATE>
08/17/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   X.INC
</CO>
<IN>
BUYBACKS, REDEMPTIONS, SWAP OFFERS (BBK)
</IN>
<LP>
   KALAMAZOO, Mich. -- International Controls Corp. said it
has extended to Sept. 17 an offer to holders of its 12 3/4%
senior subordinated debentures and its subordinated discount
debentures to exchange those securities for a package of
cash, new senior debentures and warrants to purchase the
company's common stock. The offer was to have expired
yesterday.
   International Controls also said it was advised that
holders of the debentures have formed a committee to discuss
the exchange offer with the truck, trailer and taxicab
manufacturer.
</LP>
