<IN>
TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)
COMPUTERS AND INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY (CPR)
</IN>
<LP>
   LONDON -- STC PLC's proposed sale of 80% of its ICL Ltd.
subsidiary, Britain's only mainframe computer maker, to
Fujitsu Ltd. of Japan for #700 million ($1.33 billion) was
